                        <p class="card-text mbr-fonts-style align-center display-7">Prior to her current role at DemyHealth as the Head of Strategy and Development, Adanma Anizoba supported the West African Transaction Advisory Group with ongoing research for the G4A First-Loss Facility, a funding and risk sharing mechanism designed to accelerate off-grid solar financing in Sub-Saharan Africa.<br>She contributed research to the Consulting Group on a project-by-project basis</p>
